***************
* Description *
***************  

this package includes a Matlab implementation of an algorithm used to detect 
noise pattern inconsistencies, as described in:

Lyu, Siwei, Xunyu Pan, and Xing Zhang. "Exposing region splicing forgeries 
with blind local noise estimation." International Journal of Computer Vision 
110, no. 2 (2014): 202-221.

If you use the code for academic purposes, you should 
cite the aforementioned work.

A demo script and a sample image are included.

************
* Platform *
************      

Written and tested on Matlab 8.3.0.532 (R2014a) 
It is likely that it will work on older versions.

